article_text:
Lexington, KY (40506)

Today

Scattered thunderstorms developing this afternoon. High 81F. Winds SSW at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

Variable clouds with thunderstorms, especially late. Low 66F. Winds SSE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 40%.
